name: "Survived Another Night..." by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing over photo that I took of a mysterious creature crying in our bathroom.] Despite the wail of the orange furry banshee from the hallway at night, both my wife and I have survived to see another dawn! How about you? (If you made it, feel free to buy a piece or two from my super-cheap, novelty collection! About the same price as a donut and a coffee!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
